high_descs: Walk towards the closet into the kitchen, into the closet, and over to the shelves.
Pick up the plate that is on the shelves in the closet.
Walk out of the closet and over to the kitchen counter near the microwave.
Open the door, put the plate into the microwave, close the door and heat, open the door, take out the plate, and close the door.
Walk over to the kitchen cabinet near the sink.
Open the cabinet that is below the sink, on the side with the faucet, and put the plate in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Heat a Plate in the microwave to put in the Cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, turn right and head straight, and then hang left towards the shelf.

Turn around and head straight, turn right towards the microwave.
Place the plate inside the oven and take it out.
Turn left towards the cabinet top.
Place the plate on the bottom cabinet.
